 hub.io
DTSTAMP:20260716T122601Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260915
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260916
SUMMARY:Deadline: Canon Foundation in Europe Research Fellowships 2026 (Eur
 ope–Japan Exchange)
DESCRIPTION:Canon Foundation in Europe Research Fellowships support bilater
 al research exchange between Europe and Japan\, awarding up to 15 fellowsh
 ips annually. AMOUNT: up to EUR 30\,000 per year (pro-rated for shorter st
 ays)\, flexible — covers living costs\, travel\, insurance\, research ex
 penses\, and books\; fellows determine their own allocation. ELIGIBILITY: 
 European nationals (including UK\, Israel\, Switzerland\, Turkey\, Balkan 
 and Baltic countries) conducting research in Japan\; or Japanese nationals
  conducting research in Europe. Applicants must have completed at least a 
 Master's or PhD degree within the last 10 years (older qualifications may 
 apply with supporting documentation). No restrictions on research field. P
 riority given to first-time applicants to Europe/Japan. Fellows arrange th
 eir own host institution and advisor. Up to 15 fellowships awarded annuall
 y. Deadline: 15 September 2026\, 23:59 CET (for fellowships starting Janua
 ry-December 2027). Apply at https://portal.canonfoundation.org/. Contact: 
 canon.foundation@canon-europe.com.\n\nOrganisation: Canon Foundation in Eu
 rope\nLocation: Europe or Japan (bilateral exchange\; fellows arrange own 
 host institution)\nAward: Up to EUR 30\,000 per year (pro-rated for shorte
 r stays). No application fee.\nDuration: Minimum 3 months\, maximum 1 year
 . Fellowships for 2027 start.\n\nMore: https://portal.canonfoundation.org/
 ?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
URL:https://portal.canonfoundation.org/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantde
 sk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Europe or Japan (bilateral exchange\; fellows arrange own host ins
 titution)
