SUMMARY:Deadline: Iméra: 'This Is Not Another Fellowship' – Postdoctoral
  Residency 2026-27 (Aix-Marseille)
DESCRIPTION:Iméra's 'This Is Not Another Fellowship' is a 3-month postdoct
 oral residency at the Institute for Advanced Study at Aix Marseille Univer
 sité\, offered in two semester options: November 2\, 2026 – January 26\
 , 2027\, or March 1\, 2027 – May 28\, 2027. PROVIDED: free accommodation
  in one of fourteen campus apartments\; travel expenses covered\; desk in 
 shared open co-working space\; participation in the weekly Community Build
 ing Seminar (mandatory 3-hour Thursday sessions)\; access to interdiscipli
 nary scholarly networks. ELIGIBILITY: under 35 years old by May 28\, 2027\
 ; currently holding a postdoctoral fellowship contract at a university\; h
 ave not lived in France for more than 12 months in the prior 3 years\; if 
 requiring a visa\, must demonstrate sufficient funds. Research must align 
 with one of four Iméra programs: Arts & Sciences: Indisciplined Knowledge
 \; Interdisciplinary Dialogues\; Mediterranean\; or Necessary Utopias. All
  disciplines welcome. DEADLINE: 3 July 2026 at 1pm (CET+2). Apply at https
 ://www.imera.fr/en/this-is-not-another-fellowship-application-2026-27/.\n\
 nOrganisation: Iméra – Institute for Advanced Study at Aix Marseille Un
 iversité\nLocation: Aix-Marseille\, France (campus residency)\nAward: Fre
 e accommodation in campus apartment\; travel expenses covered\; office in 
 co-working space. No cash stipend specified. No application fee.\nDuration
 : 3 months: either November 2\, 2026 – January 26\, 2027\, or March 1\, 
 2027 – May 28\, 2027.\n\nMore: https://www.imera.fr/en/this-is-not-anoth
 er-fellowship-application-2026-27/?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&u
 tm_medium=referral
